## Problem
Compact multi-profile UI was inlined and omits live countdowns (design: bar + % + countdown per primary). `ProviderRow.qml` / `PanelView.qml` exist but are unused by `main.qml`, so panel rows drift from the component intended to own that layout.

## Location
contents/ui/main.qml:318-412

## Suggested fix
Either wire compact through `ProviderRow` (with a denser compact mode) or add countdown labels to the inlined rows; delete or clearly mark unused PanelView as dead to avoid dual maintenance.

